shire (UK Parliament constituency)|Cardiganshire]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Liberal/meta/color}}\" |[[Matthew Vaughan-Davies, 1st Baron Ystwyth|Vaughan-Davies]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Liberal/meta/color}}\"|[[Ernest Evans (politician)|E. Evans]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Independent Liberal/meta/color}}\" |[[Rhys Hopkin Morris|Morris]]\n| colspan=\"5\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Rhys Hopkin Morris|\u2192]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[Owen Evans (politician)|O. Evans]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Roderic Bowen|Bowen]]\n|-\n|[[Carmarthen (UK Parliament constituency)|Carmarthen]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Liberal/meta/color}}\" |[[John Hinds (politician)|Hinds]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir Ellis Ellis-Griffith, 1st Baronet|Ellis-Griffith]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[Alfred Mond, 1st Baron Melchett|Mond]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[Alfred Mond, 1st Baron Melchett|\u2192]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[William Nathaniel Jones|W. Jones]]\n|bgcolor={{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}|[[Daniel Hopkin|Hopkin]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Richard Thomas Evans|R. Evans]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Daniel Hopkin|Hopkin]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[Ronw Moelwyn Hughes|Hughes]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Rhys Hopkin Morris|Morris]]\n|-\n|[[Llanelli (UK Parliament constituency)|Llanelli]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Liberal/meta/color}}\" |[[Josiah Towyn Jones|Towyn Jones]]\n| colspan=\"10\" bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[John Henry Williams (Welsh politician)|Williams]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Jim Griffiths|Griffiths]]\n|-\n|[[Pembrokeshire (UK Parliament constituency)|