ative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[John Henry Scourfield|J. Scourfield]]\n| colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[William Edwardes, 4th Baron Kensington|Edwardes]]\n|-\n|[[Pembroke Boroughs (UK Parliament constituency)|Pembroke Boroughs]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir Hugh Owen Owen, 2nd Baronet|H. Owen]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[Sir James Graham, 2nd Baronet|Graham]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir John Owen, 1st Baronet|J. Owen]]\n| colspan=\"9\" bgcolor=\"{{Peelite/meta/color}}\"|[[Sir John Owen, 1st Baronet|\u2192]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[Sir John Owen, 1st Baronet|\u2192]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir Hugh Owen Owen, 2nd Baronet|H. Owen jr]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Thomas Meyrick|Meyrick]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Edward James Reed|Reed]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Henry George Allen|Allen]]\n|-\n|[[Pembrokeshire (UK Parliament constituency)|Pembrokeshire]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir John Owen, 1st Baronet|J. Owen]]\n| colspan=\"12\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[John Campbell, 2nd Earl Cawdor|J. Campbell]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[George Lort Phillips|G. Phillips]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[James Bevan Bowen (MP)|Bowen]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir John Scourfield, 1st Baronet|J. Scourfield]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[James Bevan Bowen (MP)|Bowen]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[William Davies (MP)|W. Davies]]\n|-\n|[[Carmarthen (UK Parliament constituency)|Carmarthen]]\n|bg