ert Newman, 1st Baron Mamhead|\u2192]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Arthur Conrad Reed|Reed]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[John Cyril Maude|Maude]]\n|-\n|[[Honiton (UK Parliament constituency)|Honiton]]\n| colspan=\"9\" bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Conservative/meta/color}}\" |[[Clive Morrison-Bell|Morrison-Bell]]\n| colspan=\"5\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Cedric Drewe|Drewe]]\n|-\n|[[Plymouth Devonport (UK Parliament constituency)|Plymouth Devonport]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Conservative/meta/color}}\" |[[Clement Kinloch-Cooke|Kinloch-Cooke]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Leslie Hore-Belisha, 1st Baron Hore-Belisha|Hore-Belisha]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{National Liberal Party (UK, 1931)/meta/color}}\"|[[Leslie Hore-Belisha, 1st Baron Hore-Belisha|\u2192]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Independent National/meta/color}}\" |[[Leslie Hore-Belisha, 1st Baron Hore-Belisha|\u2192]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Michael Foot|Foot]]\n|-\n|[[Plymouth Drake (UK Parliament constituency)|Plymouth Drake]]\n| colspan=\"7\" bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Conservative/meta/color}}\" |[[Arthur Shirley Benn, 1st Baron Glenravel|A. Benn]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[James John Hamlyn Moses|Moses]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Frederick Edward Guest|F. Guest]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Christian Henry Charles Guest|C. Guest]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Hubert Moses Medland|Medland]]\n|-\n|[[Plymouth Sutton (UK Parliament constituency)|Plymouth Sutton]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Conservative/meta/color}}\" |[[Waldorf Astor, 2nd Viscount Astor|W. Astor]]\n| colspan=\"12\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Nancy Astor, Viscountess Astor|N. Astor]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/met