akie Astor|J. Astor]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Ian Montagu Fraser|Fraser]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[David Owen|Owen]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Alan Clark|Clark]]\n|-\n|[[Tavistock (UK Parliament constituency)|Tavistock]]\n| colspan=\"8\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir Henry Studholme, 1st Baronet|Studholme]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Michael Heseltine|Heseltine]]\n| colspan=\"4\" |\n|-\n|[[Tiverton (UK Parliament constituency)|Tiverton]]\n| colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Derick Heathcoat-Amory, 1st Viscount Amory|Heathcoat-Amory]]\n| colspan=\"9\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Robin Maxwell-Hyslop|Maxwell-Hyslop]]\n|-\n|[[Torquay (UK Parliament constituency)|Torquay]] (1950-74) / [[Torbay (UK Parliament constituency)|Torbay]] (1974-83)\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Charles Williams (UK politician)|Williams]]\n| colspan=\"12\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Frederic Mackarness Bennett|Bennett]]\n|-\n|[[Torrington (UK Parliament constituency)|Torrington]] (1950-74) / [[West Devon (UK Parliament constituency)|Devon W]] (1974-83)\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{National Liberal Party (UK, 1931)/meta/color}}\" |[[George Lambert, 2nd Viscount Lambert|Lambert jnr]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[Mark Bonham Carter, Baron Bonham-Carter|Bonham-Carter]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Percy Basil Browne|Browne]]\n| colspan=\"8\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Peter Mills (UK politician)|Mills]]\n|-\n|[[Totnes (UK Parliament constituency)|Totnes]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Ralph Herbert Rayner|Rayner]]\n| colspan=\"13\" bgcolor=\"{{