ison-Bell]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Charles Roden Buxton|Buxton]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Unionist Party/meta/color}}\" |[[Ernest Fitzroy Morrison-Bell|Morrison-Bell]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Ernest Fitzroy Morrison-Bell|\u2192]]\n|-\n|[[Barnstaple (UK Parliament constituency)|Barnstaple]] \n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[George Pitt-Lewis|Pitt-Lewis]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Unionist Party/meta/color}}\" |[[George Pitt-Lewis|\u2192]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Alfred Billson|Billson]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Unionist Party/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir William Cameron Gull, 2nd Baronet|Gull]]\n| colspan=\"7\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Ernest Joseph Soares|Soares]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Godfrey Baring|Baring]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Devonport (UK Parliament constituency)|Devonport]] (two MPs)\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[John Henry Puleston|Puleston]]\n| colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Edward John Chalmers Morton|Morton]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |Lockie\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir John Benn, 1st Baronet|J. Benn]]\n| colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[John Jackson (UK politician)|Jackson]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[George Edward Price|Price]]\n| colspan=\"10\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Hudson Kearley, 1st Viscount Devonport|Kearley]]\n| colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Clement Kinloch-Cooke|Kinloch-Cooke]]\n|-\n|[[Exeter (UK Parliament constituency)|Exeter]] \n| colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Henry Northcote, 1st Baron Northcote|Northcote]]\n| colspan=\"5\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Edgar Vincent, 1st Viscount D'Abernon|Vincent]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[George William Kekewich|Kekewich]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Henry Duke, 1st Baron Merrivale|Duke]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Harold St Maur|St Maur]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Henry Duke, 1st Baron Merrivale|Duke]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"|[[Robert Newman, 1st Baron Mamhead|Newman]]\n|-\n|[[Honiton (UK Parliament constituency)|Honiton]] \n| colspan=\"13\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir John Kennaway, 3rd Baronet|Kennaway]]\n| colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Clive Morrison-Bell|Morrison-Bell]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Plymouth (UK Parliament constituency)|Plymouth]] (two MPs)\n| colspan=\"7\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Edward George Clarke|Clarke]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Ivor Guest, 1st Viscount Wimborne|Guest]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Ivor Guest, 1st Viscount Wimborne|\u2192]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Thomas William Dobson|Dobson]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Aneurin Williams|Williams]]\n| colspan=\"5\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Waldorf Astor, 2nd Viscount Astor|W. Astor]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir Edward Bates, 1st Baronet|Bates]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Sir William Pearce, 2nd Baronet|Pearce]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Charles Harrison (British politician)|Harrison]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\"  |Mendl\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (U