ke (UK Parliament constituency)|Plymouth Drake]]\n| colspan=\"7\" bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Conservative/meta/color}}\" |[[Arthur Shirley Benn, 1st Baron Glenravel|A. Benn]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[James John Hamlyn Moses|Moses]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Frederick Edward Guest|F. Guest]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Christian Henry Charles Guest|C. Guest]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Hubert Moses Medland|Medland]]\n|-\n|[[Plymouth Sutton (UK Parliament constituency)|Plymouth Sutton]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Conservative/meta/color}}\" |[[Waldorf Astor, 2nd Viscount Astor|W. Astor]]\n| colspan=\"12\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Nancy Astor, Viscountess Astor|N. Astor]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Lucy Middleton|Middleton]]\n|-\n|[[South Molton (UK Parliament constituency)|South Molton]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Liberal/meta/color}}\" |[[George Lambert, 1st Viscount Lambert|Lambert]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[George Lambert, 1st Viscount Lambert|\u2192]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Cedric Drewe|Drewe]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[George Lambert, 1st Viscount Lambert|Lambert]]\n| colspan=\"5\" bgcolor=\"{{National Liberal Party (UK, 1931)/meta/color}}\"|[[George Lambert, 1st Viscount Lambert|\u2192]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{National Liberal Party (UK, 1931)/meta/color}}\" |[[George Lambert, 2nd Viscount Lambert|Lambert jnr]]\n|-\n|[[Tavistock (UK Parliament constituency)|Tavistock]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Conservative/meta/color}}\" |[[Charles Williams (UK politician)|Williams]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Maxwell Ruthven Thornton|Thornton]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Philip Percy K